# Simple Calculator

A lightweight, responsive calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project is part of the [FrontEnd-Projects](https://github.com/Shahbaz2104/FrontEnd-Projects) repository by Shahbaz2104 and serves as a foundational exercise in front-end web development.

## ğŸš€ Features

* Perform basic arithmetic operations: addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.
* Responsive design suitable for both desktop and mobile devices.
* User-friendly interface with intuitive button layout.
* Real-time calculation display.([GeeksforGeeks][1], [StackBlitz][2])

